    (2.0.3) always returns null (see ObjectConfig.setEncryptionConfig(EncryptionConfig))

    (2.0.3) this method does nothing. EncryptionConfig instance should be passed to the constructor of an encryption client

    (2.0.3) this method does nothing. EncryptionConfig instance should be passed to the constructor of an encryption client
